extends ../layouts/main
block js
  script(src='/js/questions.js')
block css
  link(href="/css/questions.css", rel="stylesheet")
block content
  .questions
    .questions-head
      | 职位
      a.job-title(href='/job/' + job.id)= job.title
      | 的题目列表
      a.btn.btn-primary.new-question(href='/job/' + job.id + '/questions/new') 新建题目
    .questions-list
      if questions.length == 0
        .text-center.no-questions 您还没有为本职位创建任何题目，预先给出试题有助于深入及提前考察面试者！
      else
        each question in questions
          .question
            .question-content!= question.content
            .question-level
              | 难度：
              strong= question.levelDesc()
              | 解答大概需要：
              strong= question.timeLevelDesc()
